text.tspan: Never been caving before? No problem!
Trips are £40, includes dinner and breakfasts
You don't need any previous experience as
we'll provide you with all the necessary
equipment and training, so all you need to do
is put on some old clothes and go caving!
To find out more, come to our squash at 7pm
Tuesday 10th October in New Cellars, Pembroke
